<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV42">
<l>vēṟicainta cekkarmēṉi nīṟaṇinta puñcaṭaik</l>
<l>kīṟutiṅkaḷ vaittavaṉkai vaittavaṉka pālmicai</l>
<l>ūṟuceṅku rutiyālni ṟaittakāra ṇantaṉai</l>
<l>ēṟuceṉṟa ṭarttavīca pēcukūca miṉṟiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O Lord who shamelessly went to destroy the bulls!</l>
<l>Speak of the reason [why You] filled with the red blood that flowed [from Your body]</l>
<l>the mighty skull placed in the hand of [Śiva] who put on the sliver of the moon</l>
<l>On the lowly locks, the distinct one who wears ash on the red body,</l>
<l rend="indent">who fit [the job of destruction].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
